data.description: 3.25% ASSUMABLE RATE WITH GUILD MORTGAGE $1918 per month. Seller is willing to lease as well. Located on the end of the Culdesac, this very private home has impeccable views of the Catalina Mountains on 1/4 acre large lot! Ranch home with 2 oversized Covered parking spaces and more space to park in the driveway. This home offers 3 bedrooms 2 baths and a den! Generous sized Living room with Large bright picture windows into the spacious backyard. HUGE Storage room at least 12 x 12 which would make for a great workshop. Laundry room off of Kitchen. Kitchen counters are Mid-Century Modern orange. LOVE IT! Kitchen has a breakfast bar that opens up to the dining area. Two covered patios in back opens to terraced yard with Mature Landscaping. Come and see this beauty! check out the 3D tour! many golf courses and hiking. Right down the road from the base of Mount Lemmon if you want to escape the heat in the summer. This home really is a dream come true. Come see it and make it yours!
